Strolling in Central Park from the Ramble to Cherry Hill

Some like it hot 🔥💃🏻 
Hot tips for the city:
1. Must see - Some Like It Hot at the Shubert Theatre @somelikeithotmusical 
2. Listen to @earlrosecomposer play and enjoy a Madeline martini at @rosewoodthecarlyle 
3 & 4. Stroll in Central Park & stomp on spotted lantern flies to protect the trees! @glenwhysee @alicekcash @tavernonthegreen 
5. Visit The Met @metmuseum for the Cypress tree Van Gogh Collection. You will be moved. 
6. @amnh Natural History Museum for the dinos, minerals and Van Cleef & Arpels 
7. More details to come on my childhood friend’s LES (lower Eastside) restaurant opening this fall! 
8. Fall in love at Moulin Rouge @moulinrougebway 
9. Brunch at The Smith w/ Mark @markgalinovsky future Elle Woods of entertainment law 
10. Dame Judi Dench by Terry O’Neill @fotografiska exhibit
